var book = {
	"name": "Amos",
	"numChapters": 9,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The words of Amos, who was among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22366A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22366A\"></sup>shepherds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22366B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22366B\"></sup>Tekoa, which he saw concerning Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22366C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22366C\"></sup>in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22366D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22366D\"></sup>Uzziah king of Judah and in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22366E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22366E\"></sup>Jeroboam the son of Joash, king of Israel, two years before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22366F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22366F\"></sup>the earthquake.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22367G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22367G\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> roars from Zionand utters his voice from Jerusalem;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22367H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22367H\"></sup>the pastures of the shepherds mourn,and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22367I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22367I\"></sup>top of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22367J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22367J\"></sup>Carmel withers.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22368K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22368K\"></sup>“For three transgressions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22368L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22368L\"></sup>Damascus,and for four, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22368M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22368M\"></sup>I will not revoke the punishment,because they have threshed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22368N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22368N\"></sup>Gileadwith threshing sledges of iron.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22369O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22369O\"></sup>So I will send a fire upon the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22369P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22369P\"></sup>Hazael,and it shall devour the strongholds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22369Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22369Q\"></sup>Ben-hadad.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22370R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22370R\"></sup>break the gate-bar of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22370S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22370S\"></sup>Damascus,and cut off the inhabitants from the Valley of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22370T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22370T\"></sup>Aven,and him who holds the scepter from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22370U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22370U\"></sup>Beth-eden;and the people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22370V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22370V\"></sup>Syria shall go into exile to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22370W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22370W\"></sup>Kir,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22371X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22371X\"></sup>“For three transgressions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22371Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22371Y\"></sup>Gaza,and for four, I will not revoke the punishment,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22371Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22371Z\"></sup>they carried into exile a whole peopleto deliver them up to Edom.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I will send a fire upon the wall of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22372AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22372AA\"></sup>Gaza,and it shall devour her strongholds.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will cut off the inhabitants from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22373AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22373AB\"></sup>Ashdod,and him who holds the scepter from Ashkelon;I will turn my hand against Ekron,and the remnant of the Philistines shall perish,”says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22374AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22374AC\"></sup>“For three transgressions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22374AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22374AD\"></sup>Tyre,and for four, I will not revoke the punishment,because they delivered up a whole people to Edom,and did not remember the covenant of brotherhood.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So I will send a fire upon the wall of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22375AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22375AE\"></sup>Tyre,and it shall devour her strongholds.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22376AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22376AF\"></sup>“For three transgressions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22376AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22376AG\"></sup>Edom,and for four, I will not revoke the punishment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22376AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22376AH\"></sup>because he pursued his brother with the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22376AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22376AI\"></sup>and cast off all pity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22376AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22376AJ\"></sup>and his anger tore perpetually,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22376AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22376AK\"></sup>and he kept his wrath forever.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So I will send a fire upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22377AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22377AL\"></sup>Teman,and it shall devour the strongholds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22377AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22377AM\"></sup>Bozrah.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22378AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22378AN\"></sup>“For three transgressions of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22378AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22378AO\"></sup>Ammonites,and for four, I will not revoke the punishment,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22378AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22378AP\"></sup>they have ripped open pregnant women in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22378AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22378AQ\"></sup>Gilead,that they might enlarge their border.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So I will kindle a fire in the wall of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22379AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22379AR\"></sup>Rabbah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22379AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22379AS\"></sup>and it shall devour her strongholds,with shouting on the day of battle,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22379AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22379AT\"></sup>with a tempest in the day of the whirlwind;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22380AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22380AU\"></sup>their king shall go into exile,he and his princes together,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22381A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22381A\"></sup>“For three transgressions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22381B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22381B\"></sup>Moab,and for four, I will not revoke the punishment,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22381C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22381C\"></sup>he burned to limethe bones of the king of Edom.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I will send a fire upon Moab,and it shall devour the strongholds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22382D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22382D\"></sup>Kerioth,and Moab shall die amid uproar,amid shouting and the sound of the trumpet;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22383E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22383E\"></sup>I will cut off the ruler from its midst,and will kill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22383F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22383F\"></sup>all its princes with him,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22384G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22384G\"></sup>“For three transgressions of Judah,and for four, I will not revoke the punishment,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22384H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22384H\"></sup>they have rejected the law of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and have not kept his statutes,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22384I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22384I\"></sup>their lies have led them astray,those after which their fathers walked.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22385J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22385J\"></sup>I will send a fire upon Judah,and it shall devour the strongholds of Jerusalem.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22386K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22386K\"></sup>“For three transgressions of Israel,and for four, I will not revoke the punishment,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22386L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22386L\"></sup>they sell the righteous for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22386M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22386M\"></sup>silver,and the needy for a pair of sandals—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>those who trample the head of the poor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22387N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22387N\"></sup>into the dust of the earthand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22387O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22387O\"></sup>turn aside the way of the afflicted;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22387P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22387P\"></sup>a man and his father go in to the same girl,so that my holy name is profaned;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>they lay themselves down beside every altaron garments <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22388Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22388Q\"></sup>taken in pledge,and in the house of their God they drinkthe wine of those who have been fined.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22389R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22389R\"></sup>it was I who destroyed the Amorite before them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22389S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22389S\"></sup>whose height was like the height of the cedarsand who was as strong as the oaks;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22389T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22389T\"></sup>I destroyed his fruit aboveand his roots beneath.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22390U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22390U\"></sup>Also it was I who brought you up out of the land of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22390V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22390V\"></sup>and led you forty years in the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22390W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22390W\"></sup>to possess the land of the Amorite.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And I raised up some of your sons for prophets,and some of your young men for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22391X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22391X\"></sup>Nazirites.Is it not indeed so, O people of Israel?”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But you made the Nazirites <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22392Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22392Y\"></sup>drink wine,and commanded the prophets,saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22392Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22392Z\"></sup>‘You shall not prophesy.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Behold, I will press you down in your place,as a cart full of sheaves presses down.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22394AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22394AA\"></sup>Flight shall perish from the swift,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22394AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22394AB\"></sup>and the strong shall not retain his strength,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22394AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22394AC\"></sup>nor shall the mighty save his life;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>he who handles the bow shall not stand,and he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22395AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22395AD\"></sup>swift of foot shall not save himself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22395AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22395AE\"></sup>nor shall he who rides the horse save his life;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and he who is stout of heart among the mightyshall flee away naked in that day,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22397A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22397A\"></sup>Hear this word that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken against you, O people of Israel, against the whole family that I brought up out of the land of Egypt:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22398B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22398B\"></sup>“You only have I knownof all the families of the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22398C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22398C\"></sup>therefore I will punish youfor all your iniquities.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Do two walk together,unless they have agreed to meet?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Does a lion roar in the forest,when he has no prey?Does a young lion cry out from his den,if he has taken nothing?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Does a bird fall in a snare on the earth,when there is no trap for it?Does a snare spring up from the ground,when it has taken nothing?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22402D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22402D\"></sup>Is a trumpet blown in a city,and the people are not afraid?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22402E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22402E\"></sup>Does disaster come to a city,unless the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done it?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> does nothing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22403F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22403F\"></sup>without revealing his secretto his servants the prophets.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The lion has roared;who will not fear?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22404G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22404G\"></sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has spoken;who can but prophesy?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Proclaim to the strongholds in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22405H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22405H\"></sup>Ashdodand to the strongholds in the land of Egypt,and say, “Assemble yourselves on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22405I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22405I\"></sup>the mountains of Samaria,and see the great tumults within her,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22405J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22405J\"></sup>the oppressed in her midst.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“They do not know how to do right,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22406K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22406K\"></sup>“those who store up violence and robbery in their strongholds.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22407L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22407L\"></sup>“An adversary shall surround the landand bring down your defenses from you,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22407M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22407M\"></sup>your strongholds shall be plundered.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22408N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22408N\"></sup>“As the shepherd rescues from the mouth of the lion two legs, or a piece of an ear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22408O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22408O\"></sup>so shall the people of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22408P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22408P\"></sup>who dwell in Samaria be rescued, with the corner of a couch and part of a bed.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22409Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22409Q\"></sup>and testify against the house of Jacob,”declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22409R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22409R\"></sup>the God of hosts,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“that on the day I punish Israel for his transgressions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22410S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22410S\"></sup>I will punish the altars of Bethel,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22410T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22410T\"></sup>the horns of the altar shall be cut offand fall to the ground.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22411U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22411U\"></sup>I will strike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22411V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22411V\"></sup>the winter house along with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22411W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22411W\"></sup>the summer house,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22411X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22411X\"></sup>the houses of ivory shall perish,and the great houses shall come to an end,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>“Hear this word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22412A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22412A\"></sup>you cows of Bashan,who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22412B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22412B\"></sup>on the mountain of Samaria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22412C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22412C\"></sup>who oppress the poor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22412D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22412D\"></sup>who crush the needy,who say to your husbands, ‘Bring, that we may drink!’",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22413E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22413E\"></sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has sworn by his holinessthat, behold, the days are coming upon you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22413F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22413F\"></sup>when they shall take you away with hooks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22413G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22413G\"></sup>even the last of you with fishhooks.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22414H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22414H\"></sup>And you shall go out through the breaches,each one straight ahead;and you shall be cast out into Harmon,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22415I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22415I\"></sup>“Come to Bethel, and transgress;to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22415J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22415J\"></sup>Gilgal, and multiply transgression;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22415K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22415K\"></sup>bring your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22415L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22415L\"></sup>sacrifices every morning,your tithes every three days;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>offer a sacrifice of thanksgiving of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22416M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22416M\"></sup>that which is leavened,and proclaim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22416N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22416N\"></sup>freewill offerings, publish them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22416O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22416O\"></sup>for so you love to do, O people of Israel!”declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I gave you cleanness of teeth in all your cities,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22417P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22417P\"></sup>lack of bread in all your places,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22417Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22417Q\"></sup>yet you did not return to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22418R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22418R\"></sup>withheld the rain from youwhen there were yet three months to the harvest;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22418S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22418S\"></sup>I would send rain on one city,and send no rain on another city;one field would have rain,and the field on which it did not rain would wither;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>so two or three cities <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22419T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22419T\"></sup>would wander to another cityto drink water, and would not be satisfied;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22419U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22419U\"></sup>yet you did not return to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22420V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22420V\"></sup>“I struck you with blight and mildew;your many gardens and your vineyards,your fig trees and your olive trees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22420W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22420W\"></sup>the locust devoured;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22420X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22420X\"></sup>yet you did not return to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I sent among you a pestilence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22421Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22421Y\"></sup>after the manner of Egypt;I killed your young men with the sword,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22421Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22421Z\"></sup>carried away your horses,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22421AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22421AA\"></sup>I made the stench of your camp go up into your nostrils;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22421AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22421AB\"></sup>yet you did not return to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I overthrew some of you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22422AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22422AC\"></sup>as when God overthrew Sodom and Gomorrah,and you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22422AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22422AD\"></sup>as a brand plucked out of the burning;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22422AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22422AE\"></sup>yet you did not return to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Therefore thus I will do to you, O Israel;because I will do this to you,prepare to meet your God, O Israel!”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22424AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22424AF\"></sup>he who forms the mountains and creates the wind,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22424AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22424AG\"></sup>declares to man what is his thought,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22424AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22424AH\"></sup>who makes the morning darkness,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22424AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22424AI\"></sup>treads on the heights of the earth—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22424AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22424AJ\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts, is his name!"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Hear this word that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22425A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22425A\"></sup>take up over you in lamentation, O house of Israel:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Fallen, no more to rise,is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22426B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22426B\"></sup>the virgin Israel;forsaken on her land,with none to raise her up.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>:“The city that went out a thousandshall have a hundred left,and that which went out a hundredshall have ten leftto the house of Israel.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to the house of Israel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22428C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22428C\"></sup>“Seek me and live;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>but do not seek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22429D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22429D\"></sup>Bethel,and do not enter into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22429E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22429E\"></sup>Gilgalor cross over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22429F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22429F\"></sup>Beersheba;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22429G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22429G\"></sup>Gilgal shall surely go into exile,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22429H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22429H\"></sup>Bethel shall come to nothing.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22430I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22430I\"></sup>Seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and live,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22430J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22430J\"></sup>lest he break out like fire in the house of Joseph,and it devour, with none to quench it for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22430K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22430K\"></sup>Bethel,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22431L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22431L\"></sup>you who turn justice to wormwoodand cast down righteousness to the earth!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who made the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22432M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22432M\"></sup>Pleiades and Orion,and turns deep darkness into the morningand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22432N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22432N\"></sup>darkens the day into night,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22432O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22432O\"></sup>calls for the waters of the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22432P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22432P\"></sup>and pours them out on the surface of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22432Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22432Q\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his name;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22433R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22433R\"></sup>who makes destruction flash forth against the strong,so that destruction comes upon the fortress.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22434S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22434S\"></sup>They hate him who reproves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22434T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22434T\"></sup>in the gate,and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22434U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22434U\"></sup>abhor him who speaks the truth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore because you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22435V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22435V\"></sup>trample on the poorand you exact taxes of grain from him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22435W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22435W\"></sup>you have built houses of hewn stone,but you shall not dwell in them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22435X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22435X\"></sup>you have planted pleasant vineyards,but you shall not drink their wine.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For I know how many are your transgressionsand how great are your sins—you who afflict the righteous, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22436Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22436Y\"></sup>take a bribe,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22436Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22436Z\"></sup>turn aside the needy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22436AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22436AA\"></sup>in the gate.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore he who is prudent will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22437AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22437AB\"></sup>keep silent in such a time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22437AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22437AC\"></sup>for it is an evil time.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22438AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22438AD\"></sup>Seek good, and not evil,that you may live;and so the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22438AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22438AE\"></sup>the God of hosts, will be with you,as you have said.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22439AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22439AF\"></sup>Hate evil, and love good,and establish justice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22439AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22439AG\"></sup>in the gate;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22439AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22439AH\"></sup>it may be that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts,will be gracious to the remnant of Joseph.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22440AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22440AI\"></sup>the God of hosts, the Lord:“In all the squares <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22440AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22440AJ\"></sup>there shall be wailing,and in all the streets they shall say, ‘Alas! Alas!’They shall call the farmers to mourningand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22440AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22440AK\"></sup>to wailing those who are skilled in lamentation,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and in all vineyards there shall be wailing,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22441AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22441AL\"></sup>I will pass through your midst,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Woe to you who desire <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22442AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22442AM\"></sup>the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!Why would you have the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22442AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22442AN\"></sup>It is darkness, and not light,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22443AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22443AO\"></sup>as if a man fled from a lion,and a bear met him,or went into the house and leaned his hand against the wall,and a serpent bit him.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22444AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22444AP\"></sup>Is not the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> darkness, and not light,and gloom with no brightness in it?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22445AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22445AQ\"></sup>“I hate, I despise your feasts,and I take no delight in your solemn assemblies.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22446AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22446AR\"></sup>Even though you offer me your burnt offerings and grain offerings,I will not accept them;and the peace offerings of your fattened animals,I will not look upon them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Take away from me the noise of your songs;to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22447AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22447AS\"></sup>the melody of your harps I will not listen.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But let justice roll down like waters,and righteousness like an ever-flowing stream.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22449AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22449AT\"></sup>“Did you bring to me sacrifices and offerings during the forty years in the wilderness, O house of Israel?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22450AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22450AU\"></sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22450AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22450AV\"></sup>shall take up Sikkuth your king, and Kiyyun your star-god—your images that you made for yourselves,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22451AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22451AW\"></sup>and I will send you into exile beyond Damascus,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, whose name is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22451AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22451AX\"></sup>the God of hosts."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22452A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22452A\"></sup>“Woe to those who are at ease in Zion,and to those who feel secure on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22452B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22452B\"></sup>the mountain of Samaria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22452C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22452C\"></sup>the notable men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22452D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22452D\"></sup>the first of the nations,to whom the house of Israel comes!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Pass over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22453E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22453E\"></sup>Calneh, and see,and from there go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22453F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22453F\"></sup>Hamath the great;then go down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22453G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22453G\"></sup>Gath of the Philistines.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22453H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22453H\"></sup>Are you better than these kingdoms?Or is their territory greater than your territory,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22454I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22454I\"></sup>O you who put far away the day of disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22454J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22454J\"></sup>and bring near the seat of violence?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Woe to those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22455K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22455K\"></sup>who lie on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22455L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22455L\"></sup>beds of ivory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22455M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22455M\"></sup>and stretch themselves out on their couches,and eat lambs from the flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22455N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22455N\"></sup>and calves from the midst of the stall,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22456O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22456O\"></sup>who sing idle songs to the sound of the harpand like David <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22456P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22456P\"></sup>invent for themselves instruments of music,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22457Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22457Q\"></sup>who drink wine in bowlsand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22457R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22457R\"></sup>anoint themselves with the finest oils,but are not grieved over the ruin of Joseph!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22458S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22458S\"></sup>Therefore they shall now be the first of those who go into exile,and the revelry of those who stretch themselves out shall pass away.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22459T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22459T\"></sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has sworn by himself, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts:“I abhor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22459U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22459U\"></sup>the pride of Jacoband hate his strongholds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22459V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22459V\"></sup>and I will deliver up the city and all that is in it.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22460W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22460W\"></sup>if ten men remain in one house, they shall die.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And when one's relative, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22461X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22461X\"></sup>the one who anoints him for burial, shall take him up to bring the bones out of the house, and shall say to him who is in the innermost parts of the house, “Is there still anyone with you?” he shall say, “No”; and he shall say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22461Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22461Y\"></sup>“Silence! We must not mention the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> commands,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22462Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22462Z\"></sup>the great house shall be struck down into fragments,and the little house into bits.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do horses run on rocks?Does one plow there with oxen?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22463AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22463AA\"></sup>But you have turned justice into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22463AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22463AB\"></sup>poison<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22463AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22463AC\"></sup>and the fruit of righteousness into wormwood—",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>you who rejoice in Lo-debar,who say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22464AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22464AD\"></sup>“Have we not by our own strengthcaptured Karnaim for ourselves?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22465AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22465AE\"></sup>I will raise up against you a nation,O house of Israel,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts;“and they shall oppress you from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22465AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22465AF\"></sup>Lebo-hamathto the Brook of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22465AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22465AG\"></sup>the Arabah.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22466A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22466A\"></sup>This is what the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> showed me: behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22466B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22466B\"></sup>he was forming locusts when the latter growth was just beginning to sprout, and behold, it was the latter growth after the king's mowings.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When they had finished eating the grass of the land, I said,“O Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, please forgive!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22467C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22467C\"></sup>How can Jacob stand?He is so small!”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22468D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22468D\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> relented concerning this:“It shall not be,” said the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22469E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22469E\"></sup>This is what the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> showed me: behold, the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> was calling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22469F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22469F\"></sup>for a judgment by fire, and it devoured the great deep and was eating up the land.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I said,“O Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, please cease!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22470G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22470G\"></sup>How can Jacob stand?He is so small!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22471H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22471H\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> relented concerning this:“This also shall not be,” said the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22472I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22472I\"></sup>This is what he showed me: behold, the Lord was standing beside a wall built with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22472J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22472J\"></sup>a plumb line, with a plumb line in his hand.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22473K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22473K\"></sup>“Amos, what do you see?” And I said, “A plumb line.” Then the Lord said,“Behold, I am setting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22473L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22473L\"></sup>a plumb linein the midst of my people Israel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22473M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22473M\"></sup>I will never again pass by them;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22474N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22474N\"></sup>the high places of Isaac shall be made desolate,and the sanctuaries of Israel shall be laid waste,and I will rise against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22474O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22474O\"></sup>the house of Jeroboam with the sword.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Amaziah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22475P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22475P\"></sup>the priest of Bethel sent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22475Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22475Q\"></sup>Jeroboam king of Israel, saying, “Amos has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22475R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22475R\"></sup>conspired against you in the midst of the house of Israel. The land is not able to bear all his words.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For thus Amos has said,“‘Jeroboam shall die by the sword,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22476S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22476S\"></sup>Israel must go into exileaway from his land.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And Amaziah said to Amos, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22477T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22477T\"></sup>“O seer, go, flee away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22477U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22477U\"></sup>to the land of Judah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22477V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22477V\"></sup>eat bread there, and prophesy there,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22478W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22478W\"></sup>never again prophesy at Bethel, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22478X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22478X\"></sup>it is the king's sanctuary, and it is a temple of the kingdom.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then Amos answered and said to Amaziah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22479Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22479Y\"></sup>“I was no prophet, nor a prophet's son, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22479Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22479Z\"></sup>I was a herdsman and a dresser of sycamore figs.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22480AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22480AA\"></sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> took me from following the flock, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, ‘Go, prophesy to my people Israel.’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22481AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22481AB\"></sup>Now therefore hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“You say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22481AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22481AC\"></sup>‘Do not prophesy against Israel,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22481AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22481AD\"></sup>do not preach against the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22481AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22481AE\"></sup>Isaac.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22482AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22482AF\"></sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“‘Your wife shall be a prostitute in the city,and your sons and your daughters shall fall by the sword,and your land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22482AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22482AG\"></sup>shall be divided up with a measuring line;you yourself shall die in an unclean land,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22482AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22482AH\"></sup>Israel shall surely go into exile away from its land.’”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22483A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22483A\"></sup>This is what the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> showed me: behold, a basket of summer fruit.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22484B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22484B\"></sup>“Amos, what do you see?” And I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22484C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22484C\"></sup>“A basket of summer fruit.” Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22484D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22484D\"></sup>“The end has come upon my people Israel;I will never again pass by them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22485E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22485E\"></sup>The songs of the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22485F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22485F\"></sup>shall become wailings in that day,”declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22485G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22485G\"></sup>“So many dead bodies!”“They are thrown everywhere!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22485H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22485H\"></sup>“Silence!”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Hear this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22486I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22486I\"></sup>you who trample on the needyand bring the poor of the land to an end,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>saying, “When will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22487J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22487J\"></sup>the new moon be over,that we may sell grain?And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22487K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22487K\"></sup>the Sabbath,that we may offer wheat for sale,that we may make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22487L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22487L\"></sup>the ephah small and the shekel greatand deal deceitfully with false balances,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>that we may buy the poor for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22488M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22488M\"></sup>silverand the needy for a pair of sandalsand sell the chaff of the wheat?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sworn by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22489N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22489N\"></sup>the pride of Jacob:“Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22489O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22489O\"></sup>I will never forget any of their deeds.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22490P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22490P\"></sup>Shall not the land tremble on this account,and everyone mourn who dwells in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22490Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22490Q\"></sup>and all of it rise like the Nile,and be tossed about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22490R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22490R\"></sup>and sink again, like the Nile of Egypt?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And on that day,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22491S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22491S\"></sup>“I will make the sun go down at noonand darken the earth in broad daylight.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22492T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22492T\"></sup>I will turn your feasts into mourningand all your songs into lamentation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22492U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22492U\"></sup>I will bring sackcloth on every waist<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22492V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22492V\"></sup>and baldness on every head;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22492W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22492W\"></sup>I will make it like the mourning for an only sonand the end of it like a bitter day.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Behold, the days are coming,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22493X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22493X\"></sup>I will send a famine on the land—not a famine of bread, nor a thirst for water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22493Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22493Y\"></sup>but of hearing the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22494Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22494Z\"></sup>They shall wander from sea to sea,and from north to east;they shall run to and fro, to seek the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22494AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22494AA\"></sup>but they shall not find it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22495AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22495AB\"></sup>“In that day the lovely virgins and the young menshall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22495AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22495AC\"></sup>faint for thirst.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Those who swear by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22496AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22496AD\"></sup>the Guilt of Samaria,and say, ‘As your god lives, O Dan,’and, ‘As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22496AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22496AE\"></sup>the Way of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22496AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22496AF\"></sup>Beersheba lives,’they shall fall, and never rise again.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>I saw the Lord standing beside the altar, and he said:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22497A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22497A\"></sup>“Strike the capitals until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22497B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22497B\"></sup>the thresholds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22497C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22497C\"></sup>shake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22497D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22497D\"></sup>and shatter them on the heads of all the people;and those who are left of them I will kill with the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22497E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22497E\"></sup>not one of them shall flee away;not one of them shall escape.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22498F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22498F\"></sup>“If they dig into Sheol,from there shall my hand take them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22498G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22498G\"></sup>if they climb up to heaven,from there I will bring them down.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If they hide themselves on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22499H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22499H\"></sup>the top of Carmel,from there I will search them out and take them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22499I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22499I\"></sup>and if they hide from my sight at the bottom of the sea,there I will command the serpent, and it shall bite them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22500J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22500J\"></sup>And if they go into captivity before their enemies,there I will command the sword, and it shall kill them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22500K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22500K\"></sup>and I will fix my eyes upon themfor evil and not for good.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,he who touches the earth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22501L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22501L\"></sup>it melts,and all who dwell in it mourn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22501M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22501M\"></sup>and all of it rises like the Nile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22501N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22501N\"></sup>and sinks again, like the Nile of Egypt;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22502O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22502O\"></sup>who builds his upper chambers in the heavensand founds his vault upon the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22502P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22502P\"></sup>who calls for the waters of the seaand pours them out upon the surface of the earth—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22502Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22502Q\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his name.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Are you not like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22503R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22503R\"></sup>the Cushites to me,O people of Israel?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22503S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22503S\"></sup>“Did I not bring up Israel from the land of Egypt,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22503T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22503T\"></sup>the Philistines from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22503U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22503U\"></sup>Caphtor and the Syrians from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22503V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22503V\"></sup>Kir?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22504W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22504W\"></sup>the eyes of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> are upon the sinful kingdom,and I will destroy it from the surface of the ground,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22504X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22504X\"></sup>except that I will not utterly destroy the house of Jacob,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“For behold, I will command,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22505Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22505Y\"></sup>and shake the house of Israel among all the nationsas one shakes with a sieve,but no pebble shall fall to the earth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>All the sinners of my people shall die by the sword,who say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22506Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22506Z\"></sup>‘Disaster shall not overtake or meet us.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22507AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22507AA\"></sup>I will raise upthe booth of David that is fallenand repair its breaches,and raise up its ruinsand rebuild it as in the days of old,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22508AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22508AB\"></sup>that they may possess the remnant of Edomand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22508AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22508AC\"></sup>all the nations who are called by my name,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who does this.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Behold, the days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22509AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22509AD\"></sup>“when the plowman shall overtake the reaperand the treader of grapes him who sows the seed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22509AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22509AE\"></sup>the mountains shall drip sweet wine,and all the hills shall flow with it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22510AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22510AF\"></sup>I will restore the fortunes of my people Israel,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22510AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22510AG\"></sup>they shall rebuild the ruined cities and inhabit them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22510AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22510AH\"></sup>they shall plant vineyards and drink their wine,and they shall make gardens and eat their fruit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22511AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22511AI\"></sup>I will plant them on their land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22511AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22511AJ\"></sup>and they shall never again be uprootedout of the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22511AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22511AK\"></sup>that I have given them,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;